        <item>
            <title>苦主怒斥 HKExpress 講大話 + 網民撐追究　香港快運稱得到乘客同意才調位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hkexpress-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250707</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，有網民在 Facebook 專頁「HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組」發文，稱搭乘香港快運航班 UO690 時，目擊一名家長帶同兩名中學生子女要求已付費選位的乘客讓座。事後，香港快運出聲明指因機型轉換，需按規定為未成年乘客調位，但事主其後回應，質疑香港快運，為何不讓未成年乘客與其父母對調。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250717 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9-694x163.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="163" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9-694x163.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250718 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2-488x580.jpg" alt="" width="488" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2-488x580.jpg 488w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/451412023_1016006278-2.jpg 757w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 488px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民在 Facebook 專頁「HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組」發文（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">事件發生後，香港快運回覆明報查詢表示「根據規定，當中兩位未成年的乘客不能坐在緊急出口座位排，因此與相關家庭解釋調位需要、並得到另一排四位乘客的同意後（當中包括兩位已付費自選座位的乘客），迅速安排對調。香港快運已向協助對調的乘客解釋並承諾會退回自選座位的費用。如乘客未符合相關安全規定，香港快運會為該乘客重新安排替代座位。」0&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250720 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/untitled2-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港快運回覆明報查詢表示，需按規定為未成年乘客調位（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">事主在羣組隔空回應，指「由頭到尾我哋冇人協商過」、「check-in 嗰陣時係一樣嘅座位號碼，去到 Boarding 嗰陣時被通知攔截轉位！」。更質疑香港快運「如果照 UO 所講，未成年人不能坐在逃生座位，但是他們的父母是成年人，為什麼父母不能坐在兩個逃生座位，而是硬性換了我們的座位！」，事主強調會追究到底。有網民支持事主的舉動，並批評香港快運「無恥」、「講大話」、「一 D 都唔識尊重人」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250714 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8-694x554.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8-694x554.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-8.jpg 1128w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲事主回應指「由頭到尾我哋冇人協商過」並會追究到底，獲網民支持</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250723 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10-694x512.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="512" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10-694x512.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot_20240716_-10.jpg 1220w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲批評香港快運「無恥」、「講大話」、「一 D 都唔識尊重人」（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a>）</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/posts/1032254121880675/">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a>、<a href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20240716/1721101471627/%e5%82%b3%e6%80%aa%e7%8d%b8%e5%ae%b6%e9%95%b7%e6%8c%be%e5%ad%90%e5%a5%b3%e6%90%b6%e5%ba%a7%e4%bd%8d-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%bf%ab%e9%81%8b%e8%a7%a3%e7%95%ab-%e5%9b%a0%e6%a9%9f%e5%9e%8b%e8%bd%89%e6%8f%9b-%e6%8c%89%e8%a6%8f%e5%ae%9a%e7%82%ba%e6%9c%aa%e6%88%90%e5%b9%b4%e4%b9%98%e5%ae%a2%e8%aa%bf%e4%bd%8d">明報</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/16/hkexpress-2/life-tech/travel/">苦主怒斥 HKExpress 講大話 + 網民撐追究　香港快運稱得到乘客同意才調位</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
